CIVL

Installation for Mac OS X:

bundle civl.jar and the three cvc3 libs into one directory CIVL

bin/
  civl
lib/
  cvc3.....dylib
  civl.jar
doc/1

1. Download CIVL and put it in your /Applications folder
2. add /Applications/CIVL/bin to your PATH or
   move /Applications/CIVL/bin/civl somewhere in your path

contents of CIVL:

#!/bin/sh
export DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH=/Applications/CIVL/lib
java -jar /Applications/CIVL/civl.jar $@
 